### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@organizerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2YTFkMWIxYmQ3ZTI2ODRjOTNjYmFkNmIiLCJyb2xlSWQiOjIsImlhdCI6MTc4MDI5MjU3MCwiZXhwIjoyNjQ0MjkyNTcwfQ.jj_rppLYsCL8Wg51zbVo6c-OiszjSpntFmui5jkVjgI
@transactionId=

### 1. Organizer Adds a Staff Member
# The organizer creates a staff account with fullname, email, and password.
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/organizer/staff/add
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
            
{
  "fullname": "John Staff Doe",
  "email": "john.staff@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "profilePhoto": "uploads/profile/staff1.jpg"
}


### 2. Organizer Lists All Staff Members
# Retrieve the list of all staff members managed by this organizer.
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/organizer/staff/list
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}


### 3. Setup Variables for Assignment and Verification
@eventId = 6a1d642c5fa63c6370bdebce
@courseId = 647f8765432109abcdef8765
@staffId = 67fa7e9ab921ef559102c019

### 4. Organizer Assigns Staff to an Event
# Assign one or more staff members to check in attendees for a specific event.
POST {{baseUrl}}/event/assign-staff
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityId": "{{eventId}}",
  "staffIds": ["{{staffId}}"]
}


### 5. Organizer Assigns Staff to a Course
# Assign one or more staff members to check in students for a specific course.
POST {{baseUrl}}/course/assign-staff
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityId": "{{courseId}}",
  "staffIds": ["{{staffId}}"]
}


### 6. Staff Direct Login (No OTP Required)
# Staff logs in directly using email and password to receive a JWT token.
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/staff/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.staff@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}


### 7. Setup Staff Token Variable
@staffToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2N2ZhN2U5YWI5MjFlZjU1OTEwMmMwMTkiLCJyb2xlSWQiOjUsImlhdCI6MTc4MDI5MjU3MCwiZXhwIjoyNjQ0MjkyNTcwfQ.abc_staff_signature

### 8. Staff Views Assigned Events and Courses
# Retrieve the list of all active non-draft events and courses assigned to the logged-in staff.
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/staff/assigned
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}


### 9. Staff Views Attendees List for an Event or Course
# Retrieve the list of attendees for a specific assigned event or course (with pagination/search/check-in status filter).
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendee/event/{{eventId}}?page=1&limit=50&search=&checkedIn=true
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}


### 10. Staff Views Ticket Details (Verify QR Code)
# Scan ticket number (parsed from QR) to show full ticket details.
@ticketNumber = TKT-EBCE-178029-1
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendee/ticket/{{ticketNumber}}
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}


### 11. Staff Performs Attendee Check-In
# Staff checks in the attendee using their ticket number.
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendee/check-in
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ticketNumber": "{{ticketNumber}}",
  "entityId": "{{eventId}}"
}


### 12. Staff Performs QR Code Scan Check-In (Unified QR Scan Endpoint)
# Check in attendee by posting the raw QR code data directly.
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendee/scan-qr
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrCodeData": "ATTENDEE-{{ticketNumber}}-67fa7e9ab921ef559102c019-1780292570"
}


### 13. Staff Views Check-in Scan History
# Retrieve history of all check-ins performed by the logged-in staff member.
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/staff/scan-history
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}


### 14. Staff Verifies Transaction QR Code
# Staff verifies a transaction QR code details.
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendee/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "TICKET-{{transactionId}}-someUserId-timestamp",
  "entityId": "{{eventId}}"
}


### 15. Staff Checks In Transaction QR Code (First Available Attendee)
# Staff checks in the first available attendee under the transaction.
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendee/check-in
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ticketNumber": "TICKET-{{transactionId}}-someUserId-timestamp",
  "entityId": "{{eventId}}"
}


### 16. Staff Scans Transaction QR Code Directly (Booking scan-qr)
# Staff scans a transaction QR code directly.
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/scan-qr
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrCodeData": "TICKET-{{transactionId}}-someUserId-timestamp"
}


### 17. Organizer Edits a Staff Member
# Organizer updates the details (fullname, email, password, and/or profilePhoto) of a staff member.
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/organizer/staff/edit/{{staffId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullname": "John Staff Edited",
  "email": "john.staff.edited@example.com",
  "password": "newpassword123",
  "profilePhoto": "uploads/profile/staff_edited.jpg"
}


### 18. Organizer Removes a Staff Member
# Organizer soft-deletes a staff member and removes their assignment from events and courses.
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/organizer/staff/remove/{{staffId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{organizerToken}}


### 19. Staff Forgot Password - Init
# Initiates the forgot password flow for a staff account and sends an OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/staff/forgot-password/init
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.staff@example.com"
}


### 20. Staff Forgot Password - Verify OTP
# Verifies the OTP sent to the staff email
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/staff/forgot-password/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.staff@example.com",
  "otp": "12345"
}


### 21. Staff Forgot Password - Resend OTP
# Resends the forgot password OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/staff/forgot-password/resend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.staff@example.com"
}


### 22. Staff Reset Password
# Resets the staff password using the reset token obtained from verifying the OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/staff/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resetToken": "INSERT_TOKEN_FROM_VERIFY_STEP_HERE",
  "newPassword": "newpassword456",
  "confirmPassword": "newpassword456"
}
